2017 TRIA台灣風險與保險年會 專刊
Journal of Financial Studies 
2017 TRIA Special Issue
Submission Deadline: March 01, 2018
Journal of Financial Studies (JFS) will publish a special Issue on Insurance and Risk Management in 2018. All papers presented in 2017 TRIA conference are encouraged to submit via JFS website (http://www.jfs.org.tw). When submitting your paper, be sure to select the journal section as “2017 TRIA Special Issue” for your submission. No submission fee required.
Interested authors should complete paper submission before March 01, 2018.  
